================================================================================
COMMERCIAL USE
================================================================================

AGPLv3 does NOT prohibit commercial use. You can:
- Charge for hosting, support, training, customization
- Offer premium features as separate AGPLv3 modules
- Provide consulting services around the software

You cannot:
- Create proprietary closed-source versions
- Offer hosted versions without source disclosure

================================================================================
ALTERNATIVE LICENSING
================================================================================

If your use case is incompatible with AGPLv3 (e.g., integration with 
proprietary planning systems where source disclosure is impossible), contact
the maintainers to discuss:

- Commercial dual-licensing options
- Contributor License Agreements (CLAs)
- Custom license terms for specific deployments

